ntwsInfoRFDetectMib.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectMib

revisions.description: v1.2.1, MRT v1.2: Made changes in order to make MIB comply with corporate MIB conventions.
v1.1.0: Added three new columnar objects: - ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode, - ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification, - ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrTable.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrTable
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrTable.description: Transmitter table. May contain tens of thousands of entries (different Transmitter-Listener-Channel combinations).

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrTransmitterMacAddres.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrTransmitterMacAddress
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrTransmitterMacAddres.description: The MAC Address of this Transmitter.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrListenerMacAddress.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrListenerMacAddress
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrListenerMacAddress.description: The MAC Address of this Listener.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrChannelNum.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrChannelNum
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrChannelNum.description: Channel Number this transmitter was using when this listener detected it.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrRssi.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrRssi
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrRssi.description: Received Signal Strength Indicator at this listener.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrSsid.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrSsid
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrSsid.description: The service/SSID name this transmitter was using. Zero-length string when unknown or not applicable.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrNetworkingMode.description: The way this transmitter is doing wireless networking: ad-hoc mode networking or infrastructure mode networking.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassification.description: The RF classification of this transmitter.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationReason.description: The reason why this transmitter was classified by RF detection the way it is.

ntwsInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSize.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSize
ntwsInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSize.description: Current number of Transmitter-Listener-Channel combinations found and recorded by RF detection.

ntwsInfoRFDetectCompliance.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectCompliance
ntwsInfoRFDetectCompliance.description: The compliance statement for devices that implement the RF Detect MIB.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrGroup.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrGroup
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrGroup.description: Mandatory group of objects implemented to provide RF Detect Transmitter info.

ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationGroup.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationGroup
ntwsInfoRFDetectXmtrClassificationGroup.description: Group of objects implemented to provide RF Detect Classification info. Introduced in 6.2 release.

ntwsInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSizeGrou.name: ntwsInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSizeGroup
ntwsInfoRFDetectCurrentXmtrTableSizeGrou.description: Group for one object that provides the current number of Transmitter-Listener-Channel combinations found and recorded by RF detection. Introduced in 6.2 release.
